text: Nizhneatashevo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Semiletovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 521 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Dyurtyuli. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Nizhneatashevo
